summary: Adds a retextured Giant in the guise of a Dunmer
descriptionHtml:
Anthis Telvanni the dunmer Giant is hanging around the Gray Quarter in his underpants seeking companionship.

Will this be you?

This is a retextured Giant with a Ebony Greatsword as a weapon.
He is pretty strong and has 4000 HP but is not invincible.

Makes a great packmule.

Look for him outside the New Gnisis Cornerclub.

For some reason, Atvir Dres hates him and may attck him.
author: beth
